   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>The tenth year of Tiberius Claudius Caesar Augustus Germanicus Emperor, month of Pharmouthi. From Isidoros and Maron, son of Maron the younger, craftsmen, for the syntaximon of the same [l. 5] tenth year at Philadelphial sixty drachmas in silver, 2 obols and 2 chalki has been paid, totals 60 dr. 2 ob. 2 ch; also three drachmas 3 obols, totals 3 dr. 3 ob.</ab>
